    Run the Neighborhood

    Description

    New in NBA 2K25 Arcade Edition:

    • Outdoor streetball courts and indoor courts, complete quests to earn rewards for your MyPLAYER like, shoes, outfits, tattoos, and more!

    • Ability to recruit NBA Legends to join your streetball squad and challenge players from across the globe in PvP Ranked Matches via Connection Games! Climb the Game Center Leaderboard and show the world who's boss!

    • An all-new badge system to mold your MyPLAYER into an NBA legend. Explore The Neighborhood and complete quests to earn badge points to enhance offensive and defensive stats!

    • Revamped Greatest Mode: relive career-defining moments and unlock a whole new lineup of NBA Superstars throughout the 2024-2025 NBA Season!

    • Make sure to log in throughout the year for limited-time quests and unique rewards!

    And here's the kicker – it's not just about the game; it's also about your style! Customize your indoor MyCOURT, hone your skills, and then invite your friends via Game Center to witness your greatness!

    Start your NBA journey from a young rookie to an NBA legend. Create your player and choose physical characteristics like height, wingspan, weight, playstyle, & more. Choose your position and play on your favorite NBA team.

    Become the GM and Head Coach of your favorite NBA Franchise and build your NBA dream team in The Association. Manage your NBA roster by making trades, signing free agents, scouting up-and-coming prospects, and managing your team’s finances.

    Draft NBA Superstars from the 30 NBA teams and compete in real-time with a friend in 3v3 street basketball in Blacktop Mode.

    Test your skill with authentic basketball gameplay, pick your favorite NBA team and play against rivals from around the NBA in 5v5 basketball games in Quick Match Modes. Select your favorite players and play street basketball in 1v1, 3v3, or 5v5 on blacktop court.

    Sit courtside in Spectator Mode, or play games that match the NBA season with NBA Today.

    • Play on your own or against friends via iCloud–on your iPhone, iPad, Mac, or Apple TV.

    • Hone your skills with Xbox, PS DualShock, PS DualSense, and MFi-compatible game controllers.

    NBA 2K25 Arcade Edition is the authentic Apple Arcade experience for the NBA 2K basketball game.

    Do Not Sell My Personal Information: https://www.take2games.com/ccpa

    What’s New

    Nov 20, 2024

    Version 1.30

    Introducing Season 1

    Get hyped for Seasons in NBA 2K25 Arcade Edition, a new way to unlock seasonal rewards for your MyPLAYER, like Streetball outfits, hairstyles, Tattoos, Shoes, and Connections with the GOATs.

    New Feature - Rebirth

    Picture this: your MyPLAYER starts as a major offensive threat as a Point Guard, looking the second coming of Steph Curry on the 3-Point Line, and mirroring the handles of Kyrie Irving.

    Once your MyPLAYER reaches and OVR of 90, activate Rebirth to Reset your MyPLAYER build and carve your path to greatness once again. Maybe you want to bulk up and try the Power Forward position this time like LeBron James. Maybe you want to tower over your opponents at 7’3” like Victor Wembanyama. It’s up to you to Run the Neighborhood.

    After Rebirth, you can unlock the full potential of your MyPLAYER, with the ability to reach upgrade your Attributes up to OVR 85, earn extra badge points for each badge category, and keep all of your previously earned Fans, Equipment, and Endorsement rewards.

    The Greatest - Vince Carter

    Speaking of GOATs, follow the path of the legendary Dunk Master, and new Hall of Famer, Vince Carter.

    In the iconic game mode, The Greatest, you can play as Vince Carter with the Toronto Raptors, and earn special rewards along the way, like vintage Toronto Raptors Jerseys!
